    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and grate the <strong>carrots</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely at an angle</p><p>Slice the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop finely, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
