      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a large bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped mint</strong> and <strong>most</strong> of the <strong>sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong></p><p>Reserve the <strong>remaining sliced chilli</strong> for a garnish</p>",
      "order": 2,
