      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>tamarind paste</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>tamarind mayo</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
